title: Sophie Vargas
text:
Welcome to my website! My name is Sophie Vargas and I hope you enjoy getting to know me.
I grew up in Healdsburg, California but have been living in Santa Barbara the past four years. I have a passion for protecting our environment and hope to pursue a career that allows me to fo this.
